Dialogs.Dialog: The battery's almost dead. Shouldn't you recharge it soon？
Huh？ What are you talking about all of a sudden？ ...I'm looking at you.
Why would I say that now？ ...You're an idiot.
Right now... I pass. Somehow, this kind of thing... I want to cherish it. Yeah.
Hey... what time are you coming home today？ ...Not that I'm waiting for you.
How about a kiss before you go？ ...Don't take me seriously. You're an idiot for expecting it.
You are early. Yeah... welcome back, ▲主人公＊▲.
Welcome home. Why don't you eat your dinner now, ▲主人公＊▲？
Welcome back. Tired？ Hmm, you're not fired up enough, ▲主人公＊▲.
Hey... would you be happy if Rinko made it for you next time？
Hah, you really make it look delicious. It's good.
Was it tasty？ Yes, yes, good for you.
Brush your teeth properly, take a bath, and then go to bed.
When you're done eating, make sure you wash up. Okay？
What are you interested in these days？
Sounds kind of amusing. Rinko is curious about it too.
No？ Then find something before next time. Promise.
Heh. Well, tell Rinko next time.
What kind of music have you been listening to lately？
Wow, you have good taste. It fits Rinko's taste.
No？ Then maybe next time Rinko can recommend one for you？
Hey. Can you tell Rinko about it next time？
What kind of programs do you usually watch？
Coincidence！ Rinko loves that show too.
Is that interesting？ Hmm... maybe Rinko will take a look at it.
A question. What do you think is Rinko's charm point？
That.... It's as if Rinko isn't attractive.
...I see. I'll take that as a reference.
One question. What do you think of my current haircut？ Do you like it？
I see. Actually, Rinko likes it too. Hehe.
...my haircut. I think I'll change it.
...I see. I'll take that as a reference.
One question. What do you think of Rinko's taste in clothes？ Do you like it？
...you and Rinko don't have the same taste.
Hmm. Then, will you pick out the clothes for me this time？
Hey, what are you doing right now？
Hmm. Maybe Rinko will try it too.
I see. Is that so funny？
Hey, can Rinko be with you next time？
I can't sleep. Maybe... it's because of you.
You're an idiot. Don't you think you're too self- conscious？
When I try to sleep, your face comes to my mind... idiot.
Hey... you know... that sleepover was fun.
Rinko also... yeah... don't make me say any more.
I see... then, I won't go anymore... I'm lying.
Yeah... we can go back again.
One question. Hey, does it bother you that Rinko is attached to you like this？
I see... It's okay as long as it's not annoying. Hehe.
I see... then I'll just walk away for a bit.
If you don't like it... Rinko is... idiot, don't make me say any more.
Hey. Weren't you thinking about Rinko just now？
I see. Hehe. Rinko was thinking the same thing.
You liar. You've been looking at Rinko with those nasty eyes of yours for a while now.
Hmm. You weren't on Rinko's side, were you？
Say, when do you feel happy？
Yeah... Rinko is happy to be doing this now.
I see... That kind of thing is called happiness, too.
...Rinko is happy now. I'm so happy that you are right beside me like this.
Hehe... It's okay to do this.
When you are with Rinko... no, it's nothing, ▲主人公＊▲.
You're on Rinko's side, aren't you？ ...all the way.
...I want to stay by your side.
Rinko won't be lonely if you are by her side, ▲主人公＊▲.
...we can be together all the time when we're on vacation, right？
Say... what would you do if Rinko wanted to kiss you？ ...idiot, I'm just kidding.
You have something on your mouth. Do you want me to take it off？ Oh, I'm not going to indulge you.
Hey. Give me your hand... your hands are surprisingly big...
If the whole world becomes my enemy, you will still be on Rinko's side, right？
You want to eat potato chips...？ Ah, I see.
Next to you... is Rinko's reserved seat.
Mmm, mmm. When it gets warm, I get sleepy.
Hey. Let's go see cherry blossoms when they bloom.
Such nice weather makes me want to skip school.
...it's so hot, I'm really melting. Don't you want some ice cream？
Hey. How long will this heat last...？
When you think of autumn？ That's just the autumn of reading, of course.
You know, when the leaves fall... It's lonely, isn't it？ Don't you think so？
Autumn is the time for bonfires... Such a nice thing, isn't it？
Ugh... the wind is getting colder.
Achoo. I want you to warm me up nya▼ ...kiddinyan.
Hey, what are you doing up at this hour？ Have you been up all night？
You wake up early. If you get up too early, I'll call you ojii-chan, okay？ Hehe.
Oh, sorry... Did I wake you up？
What are you doing up so early？ Rinko is still sleepy.
Breakfast？ Hah... Rinko can't eat any more.
Hey. Are you a rice person for breakfast？ Or do you prefer bread？ I think Rinko is a bread lover.
Rinko is, you know, weak in the mornings.
Hah... I'm jealous of your energy in the morning.
I wonder why I'm feeling sleepy...
Today is only just beginning, huh？
Hey. It's time for a snack. Let's take a break.
Are you doing well？ Rinko is still sleepy.
It's almost noon. Are you hungry？
Hey, have you decided what you're going to have for lunch today？
Half a day to go, let's keep up the good work...
Hey. What did you have for lunch today？
When you're full, you'll want to take a nap.
...I think Rinko will take a little nap.
Don't skip work just because you're sleepy.
It's time for a snack, okay？
Snacks, huh... Rinko wants to eat potato chips.
Hey. Do you have any idea what you're going to do after this？
We are almost done for the day. Hang in there.
Oh, it's already evening. Aren't you going home yet？
Rinko... might stop by the arcade on the way home.
What are you going to do for dinner？ You shouldn't eat only canned mackerel.
Aww, I wish Rinko could have had dinner with you.
Hey. Is there anything interesting on TV today？
Nighttime, huh... kind of makes me miss people...
Have you eaten dinner？ I'll worry about that, just in case.
Ah, homework... Do it for me, no？
Did you take a bath？ You'll catch a cold if you don't get warm.
Are you getting sleepy by now？ Rinko's... mmm... sleepy.
I miss my bed at this time of night, don't you？
Hey. Did you brush your teeth before bed？
Make sure the door is properly locked before you go to bed. Okay？
Rinko... is about to go to bed. Good night.
...at this time of the day, I wonder if we can see the stars.
You're still awake... Are you going to be okay tomorrow？
Can't sleep？ I hear drinking hot milk helps you sleep, you know？
Still not sleeping？ I'm off tomorrow... do you want to stay up late？
Isn't it kind of exciting to be up when everyone else is asleep？
Say... no, it's nothing. I wonder if I can dream of you.
You're up early. Hmm？ Maybe you were up all night？
Good morning... aren't you too early？
How many times a day do you have free time to come see Rinko？ Kidding. I'm glad you're here.
You come to see Rinko every day... I see. Hehe.
You want to see Rinko so bad... Thanks. Just in case.
We met again... We meet often at this time of the day.
You will cherish the memories of Rinko. Thank you.
Look, you're not seeing another girl, are you？ Jealousy？ It's not like that.
I dream about you a lot. Hehe, just a little more...
Hey. You've been working hard every week, right？ You know, we're almost there.
You know, I told you before. Don't turn off without saving. And yet you did it again today.
Hey. I hear you can do a lot of things today？ ...I'm kind of looking forward to it.
Hey. Have you tried anything new to do yet？
Rinko feels lost with all the things she wants to do.
Don't you want to see Rinko anymore？
You don't kiss me anymore. It's okay, though.
I said that you were the only one who was on Rinko's side. It was a lie.
Rinko is only thinking about you... idiot.
After all, Rinko can't do it alone...
You said you were on my side all along... idiot.
Why would you say that to Rinko？
Would you ever leave Rinko's side？
Even if the whole world is against me, you are on Rinko's side. Can I trust you？
...yeah, okay. Then... let's kiss to make up. *smooch*.
Ah, geez... don't make me worry.
This... looks good on Rinko, I guess？
Astrology, huh. It's silly, but I might take a look at it once in a while.
You said nice things, so I'll believe you.
Hmm... fortune telling is like this.
Worst. I shouldn't have seen it.
Your fortune is... the best？ I'm kind of bummed, but I'll let you know later.
Your fortune is pretty good. I'll let you know later.
Your fortune, not so good, not so bad, huh. Kinda boring.
Your fortune is terrible today. Well, it's just fortune-telling, after all.
I wonder if you went back, ▲主人公＊▲.
I wonder if you can wait for me, ▲主人公＊▲.
Rinko is coming back to life too... *Whew*.
I hope my skin becomes smooth.
No way！ This scale is definitely broken！
...I think I might have lost a little weight.
...hmm, this is how it is, I guess.
I wonder how much he likes it... I'm not particularly concerned about it.
This is too ordinary, I guess.
This is kind of weird, because it seems like you're getting all worked up.
I wonder if you care about Rinko... it doesn't matter.
I guess he likes the bigger ones too. Hmm.
Rinko... is always thinking about him
Yes！ I knew this was the way to go after a bath.
Huh？ Did I get this right？ Well, it's fine.
Maybe this is the way to go.
I'm proud of it myself！ I'm sure you'll be pleased.
Plenty of love inside. This can't be bad.
So guard and get ready for a small kick...
I thought I was playing against him...
Hey. Do you like being hugged？
You're good at it. That's why you are Rinko's rival.
How naive to think that would happen！
You know, when you see a cute girl, you always look down your nose at her.
...Rinko is cute by herself, or... something like that...
Oh... it's already New Year's Eve.
A year goes by so quickly.
Maybe... because I was with you？
30 seconds left... Oh, the countdown is starting.
I'll be under your care this year too, ▲主人公＊▲...
Rinko... she hopes we can make more fun... together this year.
Hmm？ You want Rinko to choose something？
Then, put the items you want Rinko to choose on the right side and the left separately.
Hmm... they both look good to Rinko, but I have to choose, right？
Geez... don't make Rinko take such a difficult choice.
I mean, why don't you just make your own choice instead of relying on Rinko？
Well, if you're not sure again, you can ask me for advice.
Hmm？ Something bad happen to you？ I'll listen to what you have to say if you don't mind, okay？
You know... if you push yourself too hard, Rinko will know.
I'll listen to everything you have to say.
Even Rinko has her down days.
You've always been there for me. Rinko is the same way.
Rinko will stay by your side until you get well.
If you are too depressed, even Rinko will feel sad.
What do you think？ Not even with Rinko by your side, huh？
Rinko, you know, she wants to see your smile.
Smile like you always do, ▲主人公＊▲！
Hehe... I hope you're feeling a little better.
Come on, take a deep breath.
Here goes, huh？ Isn't that a deep breath？
Rinko is always on our side, okay, ▲主人公＊▲？
Hehe.... looks like you've finally got your usual smile back.
You know... Rinko can only listen to what you have to say, but if you are having a hard time, you can rely on me.
Say... can I sleep next to you？
Have you fallen asleep already...？ You know... I'll stay by your side until you fall asleep.
Look, I'm sorry for being so selfish all the time. So, take a good rest today. Okay.
You look so innocent in your sleep.
*Yawn*... Rinko is getting sleepy too. Good night...
Hey... I'll give you a kiss for good night.
You know... didn't you have a nightmare earlier and say something weird？
Wake up！ ...sorry, you were groaning something.
Hmm？ Nn... hmm？ Sorry... I think Rinko fell asleep with you. Good morning.
Stretching together？ Hmm... that's a hassle. Well, okay.
Rinko hasn't been getting enough exercise lately. So let's do it together.
With your feet shoulder- width apart, stretch out with your left hand on your hip and your right hand next to your ear...
When Rinko says 1, 2, 3, 4, then you continue with 5, 6, 7, 8. Got it？
Your voice is not coming out at all.
Come on, speak up more energetically.
Next, open your legs back and forth and place your hands on your hips. Bend the knee of the right leg forward and extend the knee of the left leg backward to stretch the Achilles tendon.
Last. With both feet together, hands together in front of you, bend over to touch your toes. Then raise your body, put your hands on your hips, and lean back.
Yes, this is the end of the stretch. Did you get it right？
Want to do push-ups？ I don't mind.
Rinko hasn't been getting enough exercise lately, so let's do it together.
Hey, you know what, why don't you come with me for push-ups？
Hehe. Then, let's work hard together.
...I see. I wanted to do this with you.
One set of 10 pushups. How many sets？
Well, maybe that's about right for you.
A boy should be able to do this.
Are you sure you're okay？ Are you trying to be cool？
Challenge 50 times？ I don't think you should push yourself.
Are you serious？ ...well, if you don't think you can do it, why don't you stop halfway？
Okay, let's get started. Rinko will count, so you should speak up, too.
Your voice is not coming out at all.
Are you tired already, or what？
You're almost there, hang in there.
Yes, well done. That's why you're Rinko's boyfriend.
That many？ ...Rinko's really surprised. I'm really impressed with you.
Good workout. Sometimes exercise makes you work up a good sweat, doesn't it？
I'll wipe your sweat off. Here, come close.
Don't you think it's healthy to move your body？
Maybe Rinko will give it a little try too. Can you teach me？
Hah... I'm tired. But it feels good to exercise once in a while.
Good job. Let's exercise together again.
*Phew*... I'm sweating. I'm going to take a shower.
Hmm？ Hey, if you peek, I'll kick you, okay？
Then let's start with the sit-ups.
One set of 10 sit-ups. How many sets？
Want to play games with me？ Hehe. You're a hundred years too early to challenge Rinko.
Hey, you know, let's play a game together, okay？
I see. Let's do it another time.
Yay！ I'm not going to lose today.
Yay！ I'll beat you to a pulp again.
Hey. What are you going to do？
That's okay. I'll let you win this time, too.
You know, you don't usually get serious with your girlfriend, do you？
Hehe. Let's see how you do.
Huh？ You're quitting already？ That's too bad. Let's do it again.
Hehe. That was fun. Let's do it again, shall we？
Yeah. So, let's start from the beginning again.
Hehe. Did you have fun？ Rinko had fun. Let's play again.
I see... you had a hard time...
In a situation like this, why don't we talk more closely together？ Okay？
You told me... that you were on Rinko's side, didn't you？
You know, maybe you didn't mean it in such a big way, but Rinko,
At that time, I was so happy... because I had always thought that I was all alone in the world.
It really saved my life when you said you were on my side, you know？ When you said you were on my side,
I felt like I could forgive all the bad and sad things that had happened to me.
I know that no matter what happens, we can laugh it off together,
So now it's Rinko's turn to say.
Rinko is always on your side, okay？ Even if it comes down to the world vs. you, Rinko will always be on your side, right to the end.
Are you listening to me？ Even if someone says they don't want you, Rinko doesn't want a world without you.
If anyone says no to you, Rinko will kick his ass. Do you understand？
Let's get it off your chest, okay？ It'll be fine. Suck it up！ Why don't you laugh it away？
Together, we will be fine, because we are the strongest tag-team.
From now on, when you have a hard time, sometimes you can ask for Rinko's help.
Rinko doesn't like it when she is the only one being spoiled. Rinko is your girlfriend. Right？
